  "title": "Contract Engineer | Commercial Proposal | Water Treatment / Oil & Gas Exp",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a well-established MNC, market leader in the Water Treatment industry. They are looking for a Proposal Engineer assist their Engineering team for the next phrase of their business. They are located in South – easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities of Proposal Engineer:</strong></p><ul><li>Support the Aftermarket Sales team by preparing technical and commercial proposals for retrofit/refurbishment projects, spare parts, and service contracts.</li><li>Work with service and technical teams to gather information, perform cost evaluations, and develop proposals including required documentation and drawings.</li><li>Communicate with customers on technical and commercial matters and ensure orders comply with company policies.</li><li>Coordinate with internal teams and external partners to prepare quotations and provide aftersales support such as site services and spare part supply.</li><li>Manage spare parts inventory (if applicable) and update installed base data in Salesforce CRM.</li><li>Conduct initial prospect screening through data analysis, emails, and cold calls, and pass qualified leads to the Aftermarket Sales team.</li><li>Ensure compliance with company policies and professional standards.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in engineering discipline</li><li>5 years’ after sales support experience in water treatment / oil & gas or marine projects</li><li>Proficient in AutoCAD</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
